to install lib-gtk 3
command:
$ sudo apt-get install libgtk-3-dev


to compile gtk application
comamnd:
$ gcc version.c -o version `pkg-config --cflags --libs gtk+-3.0`
$ gcc helloworld.c -o version -lpthread `pkg-config --cflags --libs gtk+-2.0`



compiling with lpthread and alsa sound 
$ gcc helloworld.c -o version -lpthread -lasound `pkg-config --cflags --libs gtk+-2.0`



